ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你咁戇居</blockquote><br />\n所以好嬲自己嘅性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 我唔會俾自己再錯多次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次再遇到啱嘅要把握機會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfe013cd8ed88dc2068441067ad01981ea0f2e8","tid":131054,"uid":72536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T21:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>表白從來係冇十成都有九成把握先做<br />\n即係預咗一定得甚至根本已經一齊咗咁濟<br />\n純粹大家有個共識講出口咁解<br />\n類似「巡例都要問下對方」<br />\n<br />\n日本式 未開始，先表白 用落香港度根本戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但起碼試過就唔會後悔當初冇講到"},{"pid":"11cf1423df61171391b9a8e1f5f30441d96c285a","tid":131054,"uid":71266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T21:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去"},{"pid":"88abc8c8cbeedabfcb11c9a6195ac72a95e19e71","tid":131054,"uid":72536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T21:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曾經鍾意佢 <br />\n又比啲朋友抽過水 話我地係男女朋友<br />\n但當時大家都冇表示 私底下都冇傾過呢啲野<br />\n只係普通朋友咁wtsapp<br />\n<br />\n最近少左傾計 又知道咗啲事<br />\n諗住對佢慢慢心淡 